{"tid":1374992,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你班仆街 次次最後走嘅同我入黎！","createTime":"2019-07-28T02:46:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T14:24:19.000Z","uid":238051,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"07bbd73d42318e97c401add105724df147c54976","tid":1374992,"uid":238051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T02:46:52.000Z","msg":"次次都靠你地守護到最後一刻<br />\n好多謝你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n見到有幾個post解釋咗前線嘅做法同原委<br />\n有兩樣建議建議<br />\n你地睇下啱唔啱駛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 走嘅時候唔落單<br />\n最好有記者喺身邊<br />\n有狗抄牌攞身分證<br />\n必須要求佢先出示委任證！<br />\n所以 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">人多</span></strong> 同 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">記者</span></strong> 非常重要！<br />\n如果好似以下條片嘅狗<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">可以大條道理話佢冒警！</span></strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/279926822076021/posts/2364959836906032?s=689730461&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F279926822076021%2Fposts%2F2364959836906032%3Fs%3D689730461%26v%3De%26sfns%3Dmo&d=ajJRCbjZ3CJF8zdY8%2Fu%2F16crr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=5e3db590\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/279926822076021/posts/2364959836906032?s=689730461&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 試下對警察有訴求<br />\n啲犬隻成日話我地訴求嘅對象唔係佢地<br />\n叫我地搞清對象<br />\n<br />\n咁我地就搞清楚對象<br />\n前線每次喺警察出防暴對峙時<br />\n就提出一啲佢地可以回應嘅訴求<br />\n例如 <span style=\"color: red;\">要求見指揮官 要求出動談判專家</span><br />\n或者大家諗到 更minimal嘅訴求<br />\n總之就係要<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">警察當場主動回應訴求</span></span></strong><br />\n令佢地再冇藉口<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後再次多謝無數為香港、為香港人堅持嘅前線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">光復香港</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"f733a2bf18ad5f60d0bcbd234beb852b974c44ed","tid":1374992,"uid":238051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T03:02:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c2d5f31af485750ad26e35202034d1571eeb41c3","tid":1374992,"uid":49028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T03:12:43.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gerYRJr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgerYRJr.png&h=014545a9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"982f24496f5c16b374fd9cb6cb4bfff57a1e60a9","tid":1374992,"uid":238051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T03:22:47.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n今晚可能已經可以用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"056c1317584d816ceb9fae18d44d67921d5ec8ec","tid":1374992,"uid":238051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T03:32:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b66219db7041be6b1f7b6c65582d56c24c012ae6","tid":1374992,"uid":238051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T03:41:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7f7cd63ee87ac69fd53bc3a2ed580b730936c425","tid":1374992,"uid":27038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T03:45:40.000Z","msg":"屌，求下你地睇住自己丫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0695944c5718a801923b64bf185afca486d1b3a7","tid":1374992,"uid":238051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T03:55:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c6a94732c2779ebec1815f352a1f766df41848de","tid":1374992,"uid":239250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T03:56:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"52d2a02d6cfef52546622e9fcacbb6e2756f531d","tid":1374992,"uid":239